157
00:07:54,440 --> 00:07:56,470
My apologies.

158
00:07:59,520 --> 00:08:01,910
Xu... Pingzhi?

159
00:08:04,320 --> 00:08:05,680
Yes, that's me.

160
00:08:07,440 --> 00:08:08,440
Mr. Zhou,

161
00:08:09,200 --> 00:08:10,710
